Subject: Re: [T2] 12vDC vs 120v AC for a fridge (was power converter 

> A Westy fridge is either 12v DC or propane.

Depends on the year of the Westy:
76-79 runs on 12V DC ONLY.  The landline to 120V AC only runs the step down transformer. Output to the fridge
is 12V DC.
80 and up Vanagon is 3 way. 12V/120V/propane
